{"word":"G4311 - προπέμπω - propémpō - prop-em'-po - Accompany","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προπέμπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">propémpō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prop-em'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Accompany</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வழிவிட்டனுப்பு, கூடப்போ"},{"paragraph":"1. to send before"},{"paragraph":"2. to send forward, bring on the way, accompany or escort"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G3992 - πέμπω - pémpō - pem'-po/3992\">G3992</a>; to <i>send forward</i>, that is, <i>escort</i> or <i>aid</i> in travel: - accompany, bring (forward) on journey (way), conduct forth.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}